sub_title: Commercial Training Administrator at North East Ambulance Service
summary:
North East Ambulance Service provides commercial training in First Aid & related courses. All money raised through training is reinvested back into North East Ambulances. Last year we were able to purchase a rapid response car and fund a crew for a year! 

Why train anywhere else? Support your North East Ambulances and train with the 999 professionals. 

Visit us at www.firstaidneas.co.uk for courses, dates and pricing. You can book online or contact us on 0191 4302050.
